<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Maintenance — <%= appName %></title>
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{margin:0;padding:0}
    body{display:flex;min-height:100vh;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#030712;color:#f3f4f6;font-family:ui-sans-serif,system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;padding:1.5rem}
    .card{text-align:center;max-width:28rem;width:100%}
    .icon-wrap{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:5rem;height:5rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#2563eb);border-radius:9999px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;box-shadow:0 0 0 8px rgba(59,130,246,.12)}
    .icon-wrap svg{width:2.5rem;height:2.5rem;color:#fff}
    h1{font-size:1.875rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 .5rem;letter-spacing:-.02em}
    .subtitle{font-size:1.0625rem;color:#d1d5db;margin:0 0 .5rem}
    .detail{font-size:.875rem;color:#9ca3af;margin:0;line-height:1.6}
    .badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.375rem;margin-top:1.5rem;padding:.375rem .875rem;background:rgba(250,204,21,.08);border:1px solid rgba(250,204,21,.25);border-radius:9999px;font-size:.75rem;color:#fbbf24;font-weight:500}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon-wrap">
      <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.75">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17 17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0 0 21 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 1 1-3.586-3.586l5.654-4.654m5.865-5.622a6.75 6.75 0 0 1-9.128 9.128" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1><%= appName %></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Under Maintenance</p>
    <p class="detail">We're performing scheduled maintenance to improve your experience.<br>We'll be back shortly — thank you for your patience.</p>
    <div class="badge">
      <svg style="width:12px;height:12px" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/></svg>
      Estimated downtime: a few minutes
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
